title: Animated Plant Growth
description: An animation depicting a small plant sprouting from the ground. The plant has a brown root system and a green shoot that curls upward, suggesting growth and vitality.

title: Life Cycle of a Fern
description: The image illustrates the life cycle of a fern, showing the progression from a mature fern plant with fronds and roots, to the sporangium (spore case) where spores are produced, and finally to the germination of spores into a young fern plant.

title: Geometric Line Drawing
description: A simple geometric line drawing on a black background. The image features a white line that forms a right angle, creating an L-shape. The line starts from the top left, moves horizontally to the right, then drops vertically downwards.

title: Geometric Line Art
description: A minimalist geometric design featuring a white line that forms an angular shape against a black background. The line creates a right angle, resembling a corner or an L-shape.

title: Serene Forest Stream
description: A tranquil scene depicting a flowing river surrounded by lush green foliage. The vibrant greenery includes ferns in the foreground and tall trees in the background, creating a peaceful and natural atmosphere.

title: Graph Representation
description: A simple line graph with a horizontal axis and a vertical axis. The horizontal axis is labeled with a straight line, while the vertical axis has a vertical line extending upwards. The graph appears to be empty, with no data points or labels.

title: Illustration of Ferns
description: The image features a detailed illustration of two fern leaves with a visible root system, overlaid on a background of lush green ferns and rocky terrain. The illustration highlights the structure and characteristics of the ferns, contrasting with the natural setting.
